{"tid":2180514,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"阿布泰11店售千份  跨區買《蘋果》市民「另類抗議」","createTime":"2020-08-30T02:01:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T02:01:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"499c140cc8218f58e8ee49c3c4d23df3bbc1053b","tid":2180514,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T02:01:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200830/5VIVZYE7TNAKVNKNR7NTTOALAM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200830%2F5VIVZYE7TNAKVNKNR7NTTOALAM%2F&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLAESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=b5854ae5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200830%2F5VIVZYE7TNAKVNKNR7NTTOALAM%2F&h=d8d863a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200830/5VIVZYE7TNAKVNKNR7NTTOALAM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n阿布泰11店售千份 <br />\n跨區買《蘋果》市民「另類抗議」<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】國企華潤萬家旗下VanGO便利店前日起突然停售《蘋果日報》，阿布泰國生活百貨隨即宣佈「你唔賣，我哋賣」，旗下11間分店昨起各售100份《蘋果》，抵銷VanGO停賣的數量，有本已是網上訂戶的市民專程駕車跨區購買《蘋果》，以示抗議打壓言論。除了阿布泰，光榮冰室六間分店周一起亦將賣《蘋果》，深井店今日優先發售。<br />\n<br />\n阿布泰昨起在旗下11間分店售賣《蘋果》，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dVaYGt-nPlljZj45AdePBLJQi2U=/2214x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XN44SFPRWNEYRF733IE5APP2SQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdVaYGt-nPlljZj45AdePBLJQi2U%3D%2F2214x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXN44SFPRWNEYRF733IE5APP2SQ.jpg&h=8e5c252c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■在阿布泰荃灣分店，職員把《蘋果日報》放於當眼處，一小時內已售出十數份。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「社會百花齊放先好」<br />\n<br />\n對於VanGO便利店停售《蘋果》，Susana直斥此舉「係一種對言論嘅打壓」，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n位於沙田禾輋廣場的阿布泰分店，同樣有不少市民特意到來買《蘋果》。街坊陳先生直斥VanGO停售《蘋果》是政治決定。另一位徐先生亦指VanGO停售是「大家都知道咩事」，認為阿布泰售賣《蘋果》可讓市民多一個選擇，亦是一種支持方式，「賣報紙點解要搞到邊度唔賣、邊度賣呢，最希望係社會有聲出、有嘢講，百花齊放先至係好㗎嘛。」<br />\n<br />\n至於阿布泰樂富廣場分店，捧場的市民亦不少，其中李先生指：「VanGO唔賣嘛，特登嚟呢度買，支持吓。」此外，光榮冰室亦加入賣《蘋果》，更會以購入價發售，今日深井店率先有售，明天起再有荃灣、旺角、尖沙嘴、觀塘及銅鑼灣店等五間分店加入。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/OTfqCFTmp55EcAnaeupFMqsTVNk=/598x1024/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PK47XVTUIZEVZFCL6AKHXLJDLQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOTfqCFTmp55EcAnaeupFMqsTVNk%3D%2F598x1024%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPK47XVTUIZEVZFCL6AKHXLJDLQ.gif&h=f2765819&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}